window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The exciting conclusion is about to...conclude.</b></p> <p>It turns out it's hard to write a blurb for book 3 without spoiling what happened in your unreleased book 2. Rest assured, the conclusion will be exciting to say the least, with new characters, lore, and plenty of action of all kinds. Every plot thread will be tied up in a neat little bow, and the details in the book will surely satisfy men of culture.</p> <p>Watch as Daryl expands his cozy goblin kingdom and takes on the mysterious villain known as Balor in a fight to the finish.</p>"; 
